gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316bc2ef4f1a87ce1c996ba5b1e2c07a0fe642bb","tid":1745192,"uid":327938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:05:01.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"d8baf364217737c69620743cb2e4877ee41e2bce","tid":1745192,"uid":65188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1fe38d7f698e66632991dfbe7ec112c27a0fb5d","tid":1745192,"uid":65188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:06:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac847d778b4be8f2fdd9ecf86df8d896938485fb","tid":1745192,"uid":65188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8db909bb8cdcbfe182692d78ea60a5a3b8a627ad","tid":1745192,"uid":65188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:07:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"735d4d1e9989d6bb037d8238bdf3631f509fb2e8","tid":1745192,"uid":331385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:07:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02642b8f2981cfc34608dde9a28e87055b105c1f","tid":1745192,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a50d562416b277c9de71749c800f7690f48c5add","tid":1745192,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:07:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a651459a53e2d58d022ed6443c619e457c99ffd1","tid":1745192,"uid":67217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:08:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aef33412f6ab79a0f4aea6c85800ea3b8d73c391","tid":1745192,"uid":24224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba9629110ee6d84b4910fc6ade5f8c673552c268","tid":1745192,"uid":14